==English==
===Verb===
'''to sit dead-red'''  ''(past: '''sat dead-red''')''

#{{baseball}} When a batter is looking for a [[four-seam fastball]].  Popularized by broadcaster and former player [[w:Joe Morgan|Joe Morgan]].
#: ''If I were him, I would '''sit dead-red''' on this 3 and 1 pitch and try to launch one.''